name: Logo Design
description:
When you start a business, you need to create the quickest possible route to business success. A logo helps to create this by contributing to your business's visibility, credibility, and memorability -- three factors that will help your business to grow and achieve success. So, while putting off your logo development may seem like a prudent idea from a cash-flow point of view, it could result in your business never getting off the ground. It can also lead to your business folding when it would otherwise succeed.

I am here to make you business stand out above the rest. 

This logo design includes 2 initial design compositions and 5 revisions.

2 logo comps - 5 revisions - $400

name: Brochure Design
description:
Brochures are a great way to leave a impression after you have finished talking to a prospective client. 

I can help you be remembered with this vital piece of marketing collateral.

I offer either a tri-fold or a 11x17 bi-fold. 

Includes initial design and revisions until you are satisfied.

name: Stationery Design (2 sided business card, letterhead and envelope)
description:
Marketing collateral such business cards, letterhead and envelopes are vital to any business. These important items transcend your branding in a way that is easy to distribute and keep you in front of your client. 

This stationery package includes 2 completely different design treatments and we work on you stationery until you are satisfied with the end result.

We have extensive experience in stationery design and will get you what need to succeed.
